through v6.15.x), dev-python/fabio, dev-python/qtpy[pyqt5]. Solves
against the slot:5 stack revived under dev-qt/ at v5.15.19-lts-lgpl
with KDE Qt5 Patch Collection. Drop once consumers migrate to Qt6.
-->
